{"tid":1180622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：政府不是始作佣者，而是受害者","createTime":"2019-06-01T03:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T10:51:18.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":400,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0e4c42f8caeffa1f3268e84030fca846b254f7","tid":1180622,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:40:08.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗指，有市民誤解逃犯條例修訂，可能是政府講解不夠詳盡，而立法會未能召開法案委員會，令政府失去其中一個解說平台，形容政府才是受害者。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗：「可能我們講解不夠詳盡，亦都因為複雜，引起市民不同誤解，因為我們失去了條例草案委員會平台。很多人又誤解了，好像你剛才提到美國總商會，我亦不怕主動談及，他們問我政府為何繞過立法會，直接到立法會大會審議，有沒有跟足程序。我指受害者是我們，我們不是始作佣者，由始至終我們都希望有個平台。」"},{"pid":"e09c3d52118773d95dbe9a30d7b1f5b1bb0c2e91","tid":1180622,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=350099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350099&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=9a3a97a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350099&h=a43e2475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=350099</a>"},{"pid":"099dfa4db6f55ff9e2f8dfb0402d3bde15639643","tid":1180622,"uid":225130,"like":208,"dislike":0,"score":208,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"咁咪開番囉<br />\n無人叫你咁急"},{"pid":"c88a6f4d82e948ec7046f2eb962ca42f86b100bf","tid":1180622,"uid":5499,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"原告變被告"},{"pid":"a92a08b06c85af47f3c867712f170db9a5259eb8","tid":1180622,"uid":61325,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"咁係人都知你受控制既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"